WHEREAS, Ms. Lester departed this life on May 17, 2026, leaving behind a
remarkable legacy of scholarship, artistry, mentorship, faith, and service that enriched the
lives of countless students, families, educators, and citizens across Louisiana.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby express heartfelt condolences on the death of Julie
Boston Lester; does hereby recognize and honor her extraordinary life, enduring legacy, and
immeasurable contributions to the people of Louisiana; and does hereby extend deepest
sympathy to her family, friends, former students, and all who were blessed by her life and
service.
